22 (i) the candidate's first and last names;
23 (ii) the candidate's initials, if any, used instead of a first name, or first and middle name, and the
24 candidate's last name;
25 (iii) the candidate's nickname, if any, used instead of a first name, and the candidate's last name;
26 and
27 (iv) a derivative or diminutive name, if any, used instead of a first name, and the candidate's last
